                    <h2 id="mytoys-de-zieht-dauerhaft-um-zu-otto-de-0" class="pl_p50 pl_headline100 pl_headline200--lg promo_staticcontent--headline">myToys.de zieht dauerhaft um zu otto.de.</h2>
<script type="module" crossorigin src="/promo-staticcontent/assets/ft3.promo.staticcontent.module.Dealdba3.js"></script>
